gText_Birch_Welcome:: @ 82C897B
	.string "Hello there, trainer!\p"
	.string "My name is {COLOR BLUE}Dr. Colress{COLOR DARK_GREY} of Unova.\p"
	.string "I've dedicated my life to\n"
	.string "understanding what it is that makes\l"
	.string "Pokémon Trainers powerful.\p"
	.string "In order to do so, I've created a\n"
	.string "state of the art, powerful,\l"
	.string "technological marvel.\p"
	.string "$"

gText_Birch_Pokemon:: @ 82C89FB
	.string "Using Rotom's limitless potential,”\p"
	.string "\n"
	.string "$"

gText_Birch_MainSpeech:: @ 82C8A1F
	.string "I've designed a simulated\n"
	.string "environment for trainers at the\l"
	.string "highest skill level, called the\l"
	.string "{COLOR RED}Pokémon Battle Labyrinth!{COLOR DARK_GREY}\p"
	.string "The simulation is meant to analyze\n"
	.string "the will, resourcefulness, and\l"
	.string "courage of all trainers who\l"
	.string "participate. You have been\l"
	.string "specifically selected for this\l"
	.string "grand opportunity because of your\l"
	.string "experience and renown.\p"
	.string "Before you begin, I need some\n"
	.string "registration information from you.\p"
	.string "$"

gText_Birch_AndYouAre:: @ 82C8BD0
	.string "This information is confidential.$"

gText_Birch_BoyOrGirl:: @ 82C8BDD
	.string "Please enter your gender.$"

gText_Birch_WhatsYourName:: @ 82C8BFF
	.string "Please enter your name.$"

gText_Birch_SoItsPlayer:: @ 82C8C1C
	.string "Your name is {COLOR BLUE}{PLAYER}{KUN}{COLOR DARK_GREY}?$"

gText_Birch_YourePlayer:: @ 82C8C2A
	.string "Thank you very much.\p"
	.string "Please check the documentation if\n"
	.string "you have any questions or issues.\p"
	.string "$"

gText_Birch_AreYouReady:: @ 82C8C7A
	.string "I hope you enjoy the\n"
	.string "{COLOR RED}Pokémon Battle Labyrinth{COLOR DARK_GREY}.\p"
	.string "I'll see you again soon.\p"
	.string "$"
